unique_sample_hyb_protocol: Concentrated fluorescent cDNA probes (Cy3 and Cy5 labelled) were combined, ethanol precipitated and resuspended in 40 microlitres of SlideHyb Buffer #1 (Ambion). Ten micrograms of polyA (SIGMA) and 4 micrograms of yeast tRNA (GIBCO) were added as blocking agents and the samples were denatured at 95ºC for 2-3 minutes and applied to the prehybridized microarray slide. Prehybridization of microarray slides was performed in 4x SSC, 0.1% SDS and 0.002% BSA for 45 minutes at 65ºC.
